Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  你把葡萄果酱全部吃光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得千影姐做给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是爱吃也不能吃太多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一直都在强调着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样不是和小铃姐一提到红豆大福一样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:32.99,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很喜欢红豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也很喜欢烧鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这岛上已经几天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里一定闹翻天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的要一直在这个岛上生活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那边就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  只有用最后的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回可要好好完成人工呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  幸亏醒过来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家由于担心雪乃而聚集起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太专注摘葡萄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果脚下打滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们担心了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不用特意摔到别人的身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家都把雪乃当作自己的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  要说的话  我就像大家的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会说好话  小猫头鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我们也会有这种感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我稍微能有些察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两人都听得懂动物的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  一般来说都不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:13.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（你不能和动物交谈吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:18.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（读写算是基本哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  等等…怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  熊熊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  刚才还一起摘葡萄的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说熊熊肯定会第一个冲出来救雪乃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子很贪吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在附近闲逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  来帮忙寻找熊熊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  为什么我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里分为两队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  那样效率会比较高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我和行人找这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃姐和大家去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:05:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明显人数很不平衡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会啦  约会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道约会的意思吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实刚才在这附近还和熊熊在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  稍微注意点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淑女的脸受伤了该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你自己走不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是脚印吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难道是熊熊的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  只要跟着脚印很快就能找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  普通都会注意到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么快找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是熊熊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为熊熊是和我差不多年龄的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这种大叔完全不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么看都和熊熊一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是行人一直盯着看才生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这脚印原来是那大叔的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉食欲很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是和麻知姐一样年龄的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:07:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像女孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊的脸更圆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起漂亮系不如说是可爱系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮系？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看上去外表很像女生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但仔细看  就会发觉其实是女生脸的美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美少…年？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里面的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  大家无论年龄  脸  外形都完全和熊熊不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么就不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到居然会有那么多熊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没有见到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部有弯月牙花纹的熊很少见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有那么明显的标志的话  为什么不早点说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己几乎都没走过什么路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被卷入奇怪的事情里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这岛上的女孩子们都是自我主义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正我也习惯这种状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我责骂熊熊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为熊熊把做好放置在那的葡萄果酱全部吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就对她说了  「不能成为像小铃姐那样的贪吃鬼」这样过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是过分的话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说熊熊  去哪里闹别扭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我是感觉不会因为这么小的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你和熊熊的关系最好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在关系好的朋友里是不分一二的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  论交往时间的话  我和熊熊是最长的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我还只会玩耍的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃姐她们都已经开始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是六岁的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此以前我一直以为一个人玩是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从和熊熊相遇后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像一开始去捅蜂巢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河里抓鲑鱼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拥有好身材而舒展身体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人偷偷一起化妆等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了许多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都和熊熊在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此后和许多动物的关系也处的很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊转眼就长的比我大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看她这样  很胆小的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也许迷路了  正为难着  在哭吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然装作姐姐那样很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实一直都在担心着熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐立不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～熊熊去哪里了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么突然  干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空哭的话  还不如抓紧去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺刺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该在这个世界上存在的邪恶的杀气？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不应该在这个世界上存在的邪恶的杀气」是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是指那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里已经百年不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃  觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是每天都见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  那边的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不应该在这个世界上存在的邪恶的杀气」是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我就当作是夸奖的话心存感激地收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音就是这样一个傻到脑筋大条的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们  都不要出手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我和铃之间冤家路窄的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在很忙  等下再陪你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  这居高临下的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这连眼睛都无法捕捉到的快速移动的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的动作太多了  绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃一直都像这样被大家保护着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸猪排也保护着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  行人也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  小猫头鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人他并不是在保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  行人画的好糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是发表感叹的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏  和熊熊很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这要怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  请问这只熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么突然…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个岛上是没有男孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以第一次看到行人的话  就连熊也会吃惊的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衡  这样变装就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问这只熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  还以为动物很容易亲近…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样打扮的话  不就更可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然熊熊生我的气了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  居然这么难找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是离家出走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找到熊熊就是绝对不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是离家出走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「绝对不行」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上绝对没有「绝对不行」的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…也许不能说「绝对」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这样想的我  已经输了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果自己都不相信自己的力量  怎么能行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃  交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对找出熊熊给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是画
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是画的熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们的…朋·友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙·伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这只熊的朋·友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止都还OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你都干了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我难得画的肖像画都白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问小动物的话  就不会打飞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这画也许不是很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里有像月牙一样的标志…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个名叫熊熊的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年龄…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和雪乃一样11岁左右…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说漂亮系  还不如是可爱系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃  这位大叔说在那边看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个就当作回礼给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  行行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…「行行」是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊好像没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就在那桥对面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是不是有点太高了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  行人对高处不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我一个人去好了  等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  雪乃  跑着是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人把我带到这里了  我也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  桥塌了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  千钧一发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道谢的话  还早了点吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  倒过来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  让人那么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到熊熊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很担心  一直寻找着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果是互相在找对方  而迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还一直以为熊熊离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  雪乃  如她所说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  你从刚才就能听懂熊熊的话了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  说起来  我能和动物交流了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么  是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是习惯这岛的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始行行也是我们的伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教  行行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不要啦  我才不想习惯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:46.12,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HE7A573}暖和的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是最亲近的炸猪排的话  还是除了「噗」以外什么都听不出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  炸猪排的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我也只能听懂「噗」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溺水了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这回一定要好好地做——人工呼吸！
